markets.title: Will Trump make 8 trips to Mar-a-Lago as President in May 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If Trump makes exactly 8 trips to Mar-a-Lago in May 2025 as President, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: A single visit begins when the President arrives in Mar-a-Lago and ends when the President has returned to the White House. A visit need not end to be included – i.e. if May 2025 ends with the President still there, that visit counts for the purposes of the count. If the President is in Mar-a-Lago at the beginning of May 2025, that will count as a visit.
